<h1 id="hd_id3147102"><link href="text/shared/02/09070200.xhp">Mail</link></h1>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3153049"><ahelp hid=".">On the <emph>Mail</emph> page in the <link href="text/shared/02/09070000.xhp"><emph>Hyperlink</emph> dialog</link> you can edit hyperlinks for email addresses.</ahelp></paragraph>

</section>
